graph TD
    Start(Developer creates Schema Draft v2) --> Edit[Add/Remove field or change type]
    Edit --> ValidateLocal[Local validation: syntax and formatting tests]
    
    subgraph CI/CD Pipeline
        ValidateLocal --> Commit[Commit to Git Repository]
        Commit --> SchemaLint[Schema Linter check]
        SchemaLint --> SRCompatCheck["Registry Compatibility API Check: POST /compatibility"]
    end

    SRCompatCheck -->|Fails Validation| Fix[Reject PR / Developer fixes schema]
    Fix --> Edit

    SRCompatCheck -->|Passes Validation| Approve[Merge PR to Main]
    Approve --> DeploySR[Deploy Schema Registry: Auto-register or CLI deploy]
    
    DeploySR --> ProdRun[Production Execution]
    
    subgraph Runtime Evolution
        ProdRun --> ProdProduce[Producers write v2 payloads]
        ProdProduce --> ProdConsume[Consumers read v1 & v2 events typesafely]
    end

    ProdConsume --> End(Cycle Complete)

    style SRCompatCheck fill:#f96,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Fix fill:#fbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style DeploySR fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
